OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore strikes planned as    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fteachers reject pay offer  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Teachers in England will strike on     
OL,6, Thursday 27 April and Tuesday 2 May    
OL,7, after members of the UK's largest      
OL,8, education union overwhelmingly rejected
OL,9, a pay offer.                           
OL,11,FThe National Education Union described 
OL,12,Fthe offer as "insulting" and has       
OL,13,F"united the profession in its outrage".
OL,15,FThe results of the NEU ballot found    
OL,16,Fthat 98% of NEU members were in favour 
OL,17,Fof turning the deal down.              
OL,19,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan said
OL,20,Fit was "extremely disappointing".      
